text: Chicoloapan or Chicoloapan de Juárez is a town in the Mexican state of Mexico. It is the municipal seat of and largest city in the Chicoloapan Municipality. In 2010, 168,591 people lived there. ==References== Category:Towns in Mexico Category:Settlements in Mexico (state) Category:Municipality seats in Mexico (state)
